name: [GM]00
discription: After many disappointing experiences as a play, decided to create my own Renewal Ragnarok server. Since I started this project, I quickly fell in love with it, and now actively work towards improving YYRO every day. It makes me so incredibly happy to know that while I may not have gotten to enjoy to Ragnarok Online experience I wish I got, we're able to provide such an experience to our players.

name: [GM]YY
discription: Hi! I am a developer in charge of all heavy-duty coding. When I'm not microwaving tea of taking care of my two little kids, I verify and fix bugs, and test and port content from twRo and kRo. When I can, I also spend time in-game, where I like to help players.

name: [GM]Mily
discription: Hi, it’s Rumble! I’m a content developer who learned to code years ago because of RO, back when instanced dungeons were just arriving. Helped porting the 3rd job classes as they were being released on kRO and recently came out of a RO hiatus. Now, I’m focused on developing new game modes and I’m excited to bringing these ideas to life!
